---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
import ReviewHero from "../../components/ReviewHero.astro";

export const title = "It's for sale.";
export const description = "Explore the heartfelt farewell of a beloved 2015 Jeep Wrangler JK named Overclock, now seeking a new home.";
const youtubeId = "MdwPEBLQ7m8";
const buyLink = null;
const buyText = "View Product \u2192";
const discountCode = null;
const discountText = null;
export const date = "2020-04-09";
export const specs = [
  {
    "label": "Category",
    "value": "Builds, Mods, Off-Road"
  },
  {
    "label": "Brand",
    "value": "Jeep"
  },
  {
    "label": "Product",
    "value": "Wrangler JK"
  },
  {
    "label": "Use Case",
    "value": "Built for off-road adventures"
  }
];
const externalLinks = [{"label": "I hate this. I want to stay in the Jeep community. I also want to keep this channel running. But it's time for OVERCLOCK3D to go to a new home.", "url": "https://www.facebook.com/marketplace/item/1604264549721756/"}];
---

<SiteLayout title={`${title} | o3djeeps`} description={description}>

<article>

<ReviewHero
  title={title}
  description={description}
  youtubeId={youtubeId}
  buyLink={buyLink}
  buyText={buyText}
  discountCode={discountCode}
  discountText={discountText}
  showPromo={Boolean(discountCode && buyLink)}
  specs={specs}
  externalLinks={externalLinks}
  date={date}
/>

<h2>Overview</h2><p>In the world of Jeep enthusiasts, the connection between a driver and their vehicle is often deep and personal. Today, we bring you a poignant discussion surrounding a 2015 Jeep Wrangler JK known affectionately as Overclock, which is currently up for sale. This is not just a vehicle; it's a showcase of love, upgrades, and countless adventures—all now seeking a new owner. As the owner transitions to a new life chapter relocating from Maryland to Florida, the sentiment of letting go resonates throughout the community.</p><h2>Main Points</h2><p>Overclock's story begins with its captivating Anvil color, a limited edition hue that shifts beautifully in varying light conditions. This unique quality not only makes the Jeep a standout but also highlights the passion Jeep owners have for rare models. With a brand new engine that only has 68 miles on it, replaced under warranty, this Jeep promises reliability and performance moving forward. The original owner’s proactive maintenance ensures that potential buyers can enjoy a hassle-free experience.</p><p>However, the allure of Overclock goes beyond its engine. The Jeep is equipped with a plethora of high-end modifications that significantly enhance its off-road capabilities. A Dyna-Trac Pro Rock 44 axle kit, ARB air compressor, 37-inch tires, and King remote reservoir shocks are just a few notable upgrades. Each component was carefully chosen to create a sturdy build that stands ready for any adventure, whether you're tackling rugged trails or cruising through city streets.</p><p>Besides performance aspects, it’s also equipped with stylish and functional features. HID headlamps with angel eyes, custom grille inserts, and a well-thought-out interior filled with locking storage solutions demonstrate the thoughtful design behind this setup. The owner has effectively blended form and function to provide an enjoyable experience for both daily driving and off-road excursions.</p><h2>Practical Implications</h2><p>For potential buyers and fellow enthusiasts, Overclock represents an opportunity to own a meticulously cared-for vehicle loaded with upgrades. The price point of $35,000 reflects not just the vehicle but the thousands invested in modifications aimed at enhancing performance and comfort. The perspective from the seller brings a personal touch, highlighting the challenges of moving and downsizing a collection of vehicles. It's a reminder that while we may release one vehicle, the memories created and the enthusiasm for the Jeep community persist.</p><h2>Key Takeaways</h2><ul><li>Overclock is more than just a Jeep; it's a labor of love, offering a glimpse into the passion and dedication that goes into building a performance vehicle.</li><li>With a new engine and a multitude of upgrades, this Jeep stands as a prime example of what can be achieved with thoughtful modifications.</li><li>Though selling can be tough, the anticipation of passing it on to another enthusiast allows for the spirit of the vehicle to live on.</li><li>For any off-road enthusiast looking to jump into a fully equipped, reliable rig, Overclock represents a fantastic opportunity.</li></ul>

</article>

</SiteLayout>
